title: *$500 off first month's rent* Spacious Corner Apartment @ Parkway West
posting_body: ['Property Address', '4556 46th Avenue S - 203 | Minneapolis, MN 55406', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', "Sign a lease today and get $500 off your first month's rent!", 'This stunning 1BR apartment sits in the corner of the building and has large windows that bring in a lot of natural sunlight!', 'Your new home features a large, open Euro-style kitchen with a dishwasher and a moveable center island.', "The kitchen leads into a huge great room that's perfect for hosting guests or relaxing after a long day.", "You'll also have access to the fitness center on the 2nd floor, and the large patio with a grill on the 4th floor.", 'Walk or bike the trails, relax in the park, frequent the shops, or meet your friends at the nearby pubs and cafes.', 'The Longfellow neighborhood is always bustling with activity.', 'Parkway West is on the Metro Transit A-Line and just over the Ford Parkway bridge you can enjoy everything the Highland Park neighborhood offers in St. Paul.', 'You will love being in the middle of everything!', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Final price subject to change pending walk-through inspection.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Fitness Center', 'Community Lounge and Patio', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Elevator', 'Unique Floor Plan', 'Open Design Layout and Concept', 'Washer and Dryer in Unit', 'Dishwasher', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 774', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,495.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
